{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sdbmhash"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This algorithm was created for sdbm (a public-domain reimplementation of ndbm) database library."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it was found to do well in scrambling bits, causing better distribution of the keys and fewer splits."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it also happens to be a good general hashing function with good distribution."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the actual function is hash(i) = hash(i - 1) * 65599 + str[i];"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"what is included below is the faster version used in gawk."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[there is even a faster, duff-device version] the magic prime constant 65599 (2^6 + 2^16 - 1)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was picked out of thin air while experimenting with many different constants."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this is one of the algorithms used in berkeley db (see sleepycat) and elsewhere."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String\/sdbmhash"},"abstract":[{"text":"Hashed string","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdbmhash","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"extendedModule":"Swift","externalID":"s:SS11SwiftExtrasE8sdbmhashSivp","role":"symbol","title":"sdbmhash","symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"relatedModules":["Swift"],"name":"SwiftExtras"}]},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras","doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift","doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string\/sdbmhash"]}],"references":{"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[],"title":"SwiftExtras","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift/String/sdbmhash":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Hashed string"}],"url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string\/sdbmhash","title":"sdbmhash","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdbmhash","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String\/sdbmhash","type":"topic"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift/String":{"abstract":[],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"extension"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"String"}],"title":"String","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift":{"abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"Swift","type"